		<h3> Background </h3> 
				 <p>I received my PhD from <a href="http://www.public.asu.edu/~xiahu/rankings1.jpg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Arizona State University</a> under the  supervision of Dr.  <a href="http://www.public.asu.edu/~huanliu/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Huan Liu</a>. I received my Master and Bachelor degrees from  <a href="http://www.buaa.edu.cn/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Beihang University</a>. Before my current position, I worked as a postdoctoral researcher at Arizona State University and Phoenix Veteran Affairs Health Care System, a research intern at <a href="http://research.microsoft.com/en-us/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Microsoft Research</a>, and a visiting student at <a href="http://www.nus.edu.sg/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">National University of Singapore</a> with Dr. <a href="http://www.comp.nus.edu.sg/~chuats/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Tat-Seng Chua</a>. </p>
